---
title: Chermoula Chicken with Roasted Veggies & Lemon Yoghurt
description: With chermoula spice blend coating the chicken and a mouth-watering mix of lemon yoghurt, rice studded with currants and sweet roasted veggies, this meal is sure to bring major excitement to the dinner table.
